{
  "texts": [
    "Just a quick survey among colleagues in my office resulted in almost the entire spectrum of opinions on using GenAI for academic writing.",
    "On one end a researcher that uses it daily, and on the other end one that is principally against using it.",
    "The reason for boycotting?",
    "It would be cheating to use an GenAI to write up your research.",
    "Whether this is indeed cheating or not is actually irrelevant, as this disagreement shows that researchers have different opinions on what \"good science\" is, and what you can and cannot use whilst retaining your research integrity."
  ]
}